"A 4 and 2 combination is a sign that you have help available from spirit and the angels in making your desired transitions.  All you need to do is ask.  At this time you may need to be reminded that you are never alone as your angels and guides are always with you."
"The 2 and 4 number combination is a message from your angels that they are working very closely with you at the moment, and their greatest wish is to see you succeed on your path.  They stand by your side offering assistance when requested.  You are encouraged to ask for help whenever you feel the need."
